FW Reports on GTC ClusterDarron Listed below are the directions to get into the reporting Let me know if you need any additional information Thanks TARA Original Message From Lees Lisa Sent Thursday November PM To Perkins Regina George Fraisy Johnson Adam Sweitzer Tara Moorer Torrey Matthew Stephen Cc Denny Jennifer Puthigai Savita Subject Reports on GTC Cluster For back door access to EOL Reports please follow the steps outlined below Go to Choose EnronOnline GTC Loader Cluster from the drop down list Login using your regular NT account Choose StartProgramsWindows NT Explorer Navigate to cClickTradeReports Double Click on Reports Login to Reports as normal

Coast Energy Canada and Coast Energy Group contract question Cc Tana Per my voice mail I received a call from Gregg Thompson with Coast energy Canada and US He has several questions regarding the base contract that they have with Enron and EnronOnline For example if their users logged into EOL under Coast Canada and transacted on an US product what underlying agreement would be governed From my conversation with Gregg I believe that they are trying to figure out what contract applies to what entity when transacted on EOL If you could give them a call they would really appreciate it Thanks for your time He can be reached at Thanks TARA

RE Straddle Problem Cc Dan and Larry I wanted to let you know that we have found out what the problem was regarding these deals Tonight we will create new products in order for these deals to bridge correctly tomorrow As a result all straddle products should be captured correctly with two legs tomorrow I apologize fro the inconvenience Thanks TARA Original Message From Thibaut Dan Sent Thursday October PM To Sweitzer Tara Cc McLaughlin Jr Errol Subject RE Straddle Problem Tara I have booked the deals correctly and reference the EOL IDs Additionally deal confirms has done their thing and notified the cp Please let me know if my trader Larry May or I need to do anything else to preempt this from happening in the future Thanks for your quick response to this problem Dan Original Message From Sweitzer Tara Sent Thursday October PM To Thibaut Dan Cc Moorer Torrey Subject RE Straddle Problem It will have to be someone from comformations We never interact with the customer Also This fix will only affect deals on a go forward basis All the deals that have been booked incorrectly will need to be fixed by risk Myself and Tagg IT are still working on the issue and will be in contact with you as soon as it has bee fixed Thanks TARA Original Message From Thibaut Dan Sent Thursday October AM To Sweitzer Tara Subject RE Straddle Problem Thanks Can someone let the CP know that the deals are good Do yall interface with CP If not deal confirmations could but they need the deal details Please let me know Thanks Dan Original Message From Sweitzer Tara Sent Thursday October AM To May Larry Thibaut Dan Riordan Sean Cheung Cecilia Rivera Oscar Cc Moorer Torrey Subject Straddle Problem Dan I wanted to let you know that we are working on the problem that we are having with the straddle deals being booked into Tagg I also wanted to bring to your attention that these deals tested correctly in Tagg Stage so we are trying to sort out what is happening in Production I am working with Tagg IT to resolve the issue I will keep you posted Thanks TARA

Straddle Problem Cc Dan I wanted to let you know that we are working on the problem that we are having with the straddle deals being booked into Tagg I also wanted to bring to your attention that these deals tested correctly in Tagg Stage so we are trying to sort out what is happening in Production I am working with Tagg IT to resolve the issue I will keep you posted Thanks TARA

RE Locations for Patrice Thurston Cc Cora Melba and I have a few questions regarding your email We left you a voice mail around Please call us as soon as you get this email and we can discuss Also we are putting these products out on production because we have questions regarding the setup of Patrices products Please call us Thanks TARA Original Message From Pendergrass Cora Sent Wednesday October PM To Sweitzer Tara Cc Mims Patrice L Simpson James Subject RE Locations for Patrice Thurston Importance High Originally we sent you this but now this is what we need to have set up We asked for PGLCNBPLNBPL should be NBPLPeoples Northern Border Manhattan PGLCNGPLNGPL should be NGPLPeoples NGPL Peoples PGLCTTPTTP should be PGLCTTPTTP This was formerly PGLCNGPL which is and INCORRECT meter on PGLCs side PGLCTTPTTP is the POOL for PGLC This product should be called Peoples Pool on EOL rather than PGLCNGPLNon Pool Let me know Original Message From Sweitzer Tara Sent Wednesday October PM To Truong Dat Pendergrass Cora Doan Jad Lozano Melba Subject FW Locations for Patrice Thurston Dat Can you get me screen prints of these two deals They are in Sitara Parallel Thanks TARA Original Message From Pendergrass Cora Sent Wednesday October PM To Sweitzer Tara Doan Jad Cc Lozano Melba Subject RE Locations for Patrice Thurston I am trying to get into Sitara Parallel but Im not having any luck any idea who to call about that one Thanks Cora Original Message From Sweitzer Tara Sent Wednesday October PM To Doan Jad Pendergrass Cora Cc Lozano Melba Subject FW Locations for Patrice Thurston Cora and Jad Please take a look at these two test deals that Patrice has requested I am still waiting on global to get the tradezone TTP added I will let you know as soon as I hear from Sylvia Campos In the mean time please take a look at the other two test deals in sitara Parallel The deal numbers are as follows NicorEDubuque NBPLManhattan Please get back to me ASAP if these two products look good and we can release them for production Thanks TARA Original Message From Pendergrass Cora Sent Wednesday October AM To Sweitzer Tara Subject RE Locations for Patrice Thurston Everything right now is currently mapped to PGLCNGPL when deals are done on EOL THere are deals out there right now with this meter for future months These deals will need to be changed to PGLCTTPTTP manually The meter PGLCNGPL should not be used after these new trade zones are set up This is how it needs to be set up PIPETRADE ZONEFACILITY PGLCNGPLNGPL PGLCNBPLNBPL PGLCTTPTTP We need to set up this trade zone Spoke with Russ Severenson Original Message From Sweitzer Tara Sent Wednesday October AM To Pendergrass Cora Lozano Melba Subject FW Locations for Patrice Thurston Importance High Can you get me the following infromation that I requested from Jad Thanks TARA Original Message From Doan Jad Sent Wednesday October AM To Sweitzer Tara Subject FW Locations for Patrice Thurston Importance High Jad I need the Pipe Trade zone and Facility number for these locations as soon as possible Patrice Thurston is asking for this products ASAP Call me if you have any problems getting this information to me Original Message From Lozano Melba Sent Monday October PM To Moorer Torrey Cc Sweitzer Tara Subject Locations for Patrice Thurston Importance High Torrey I know you had asked me in the past to go ahead and pass on to you traders which are pressuring us to get stuff out Do you mind calling or emailing Patrice ThurstonMims and explaining to her the enormous back log we have in the testing area and the under staffed that we are Let me know if you any questions Products Oct US Gas Phy Fwd Firm Locations Melba NIGNNG US Gas Phy NicorEDubuque PGLCTTPTTP US Gas Phy PGLCNGPL NonPool NBPLPeoples US Gas Phy NBPLManhattan Thanks Melba
